Eric Winter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Winter 0 Eric Barrett Winter (born July 17, 1976) is an American actor, producer, author and former fashion model, best known for his television roles as FBI Special Agent Craig O'Laughlin on CBS drama series The Mentalist (2010–2012), and Dash Gardiner on the Lifetime fantasy-drama series Witches of East End (2013–2014). He is known for his film roles in Harold Kumar Escape from Guantanamo Bay (2008) and The Ugly Truth (2009).
